 - Fix parsing to allow CR or LF at buffer end. #24
   Contributor: Ben Tyler

0.24 2015-06-02T22:18:12+0200
 - Fix default nick only contains [a-z] and "_".

0.23 2015-06-02T00:46:24+0200
